    "en": {
      "title": "Tension in Hutton: Colombo Road closed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "About 2,000 customers lined up to buy kerosene at the Chipetco Fuel Station in Hutton, blocking Hutton Colombo Main Road in front of the petrol station.",
        "Consumers protesting in the Hutton area have said they have not had a stock of kerosene since last (09) and return home empty-handed, waiting in line for hours every day.",
        "Hutton police have taken action to divert traffic on the Hutton-Colombo main road due to the protest."
      ],
